1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome back to Alpha Zone where football meets AI.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,500
Today I want to show you something wild about expected goals.

3
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:15,000
Most people think xG measures how good a shot was, but that's only half the story.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
The model actually learns from thousands of historical shots to estimate probability.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:27,500
And here is the part nobody talks about: it is terrible at rare events like long shots.
